WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.080
Rochester, the city of imagination and innovation through the optical lenses of a photographic

00:06.080 --> 00:12.880
display, a city that has been curated to be the world's imaging center thanks to the involvement of

00:12.880 --> 00:19.600
three major companies that originate from the area, Xerox, Kodak, and Baush, and Lomb.

00:20.400 --> 00:26.000
These companies have been labeled as the Big Three as they paved the way for innovation in optical

00:26.000 --> 00:31.840
and photographic sciences and inserted the foundations of future technological developments.

00:32.720 --> 00:38.160
Although much time has passed since these companies have been established, even in current times,

00:38.160 --> 00:41.920
they still hold an unforgettable presence in the flower city.

